# Mediatrix, environment configuration example.
#
# Copy this file to `.env.local` (which is gitignored) and fill in the
# values that apply to your machine. The Makefile sources `.env.local`
# automatically if it exists.

# Absolute path to the canonical Mariology markdown corpus
# (thirteen .md files). If unset, the pipeline falls back to
# ./corpus/mariology/ inside the repository root.
#
# MARIOLOGY_CORPUS=/absolute/path/to/your/mariology/markdown

# Local preview server port. Default is 8000.
# PORT=8000
